      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right owner? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, drives, and could make a great budget runabout, first car, or project for someone handy. It\u2019s an honest, no-frills vehicle being sold as a practical option for anyone who wants dependable basic transportation without spending a fortune. If you appreciate a straightforward deal and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this could be a really worthwhile buy.",
      "price": 4950.0,
