      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a strong-running engine, smooth-shifting transmission, and good core mechanicals. This car shows wear, but it still offers dependable basic transportation and a well-sorted drivetrain for someone who appreciates simple, proven hardware. Ideal for a handy owner, commuter backup, or weekend revive, with plenty of usable life left for the money.",
