      "description": "This car has the kind of old-school character you notice right away\u2014the sort of ride that feels honest, seasoned, and ready for its next chapter. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone who appreciates a vehicle with personality, whether you want a budget-friendly daily, a practical backup, or a rewarding project to make your own. There\u2019s a lot of charm in its straightforward nature, and at this price point, it offers a rare chance to get behind the wheel without stretching your budget. If you see potential instead of just polish, this one has a lot to offer.",
